Wire Diagram:

RPi Connector   || PPORT @ pluto-p board
-------------------------------------------
MOSI 19         || Data0    2
MISO 21         || Data1    3
SCLK 23         || nStrobe  1
CE0  24         || Init    16

GPIO25  22      || Data2    4

GND  20,25      || GND     18-25


Compiling the Pluto SPI driver for the RasPi:

    sudo comp --install pluto_servo_rpspi.comp
    sudo comp --install pluto_step_rpspi.comp


